text: Institut d'études politiques de Saint-Germain-en-Laye is a special university in France. The school is in Saint-Germain-en-Laye. It was created in 2013. It is a specialist in the fields of economics, administration, social sciences and politics.Le dixième Sciences Po ouvre ses portes à Saint-Germain-en-Laye ==References== == More reading == * Sciences Po Saint-Germain-en-Laye website Category:Education in France
